Doxycycline compared with prednisolone therapy for patients with bullous 
pemphigoid: cost-effectiveness analysis of the BLISTER trial.

Mason JM(1), Chalmers JR(2), Godec T(3), Nunn AJ(3), Kirtschig G(2), Wojnarowska 
F(4), Childs M(5), Whitham D(5), Schmidt E(6), Harman K(7), Walton S(8), Chapman 
A(9), Williams HC(2); U.K. Dermatology Clinical Trials Network BLISTER Study 
Group.

Author information:
