(2)Centre of Evidence Based Dermatology, University of Nottingham, Nottingham, 
NG7 2NR, U.K.
(3)MRC Clinical Trials Unit at UCL, Aviation House, 125 Kingsway, London, WC2B 
6NH, U.K.
(4)Nuffield Department of Clinical Medicine, University of Oxford, Oxford, OX3 
