(7)Department of Dermatology, St Vincent's Hospital, Darlinghurst, Sydney, NSW, 
Australia.
(8)Department of Dermatology, University of Colorado Anschutz Medical Campus, 
Aurora, CO, USA; Department of Epidemiology, Colorado School of Public Health, 
